title: fix different access modifier in EmbeddingStoreIT and EmbeddingStoreW…

body:

## Issue
<!-- Please specify the ID of the issue this PR is addressing. For example: "Closes #1234" or "Fixes #1234" -->
Closes #1919 

## Change
<!-- Please describe the changes you made. -->

* Change access modifier of `should_filter_by_metadata_not` from default to protected in `EmbeddingStoreWithFilteringIT`.
* Change access modifier of `TEST_UUID2` from default to protected in `EmbeddingStoreIT`.
